00:16:53,160 --> 00:16:55,830
...even though you give me[br]the feelings.

258
00:16:57,560 --> 00:16:59,110
I had no idea.

259
00:17:01,120 --> 00:17:03,110
I can always find another masseuse.

260
00:17:03,600 --> 00:17:04,550
Really?

261
00:17:04,800 --> 00:17:06,670
Yeah, really.

262
00:17:11,800 --> 00:17:12,750
What?

263
00:17:12,960 --> 00:17:15,230
Suddenly I'm very aware I'm naked.

264
00:17:17,600 --> 00:17:18,630
Quiet down.

265
00:17:22,160 --> 00:17:24,510
Mr. Simon's been waiting...[br]Oh, my God!

266
00:17:24,760 --> 00:17:26,150
Why wasn't I offered that?

267
00:17:26,800 --> 00:17:29,070
I'd definitely pay more for that.

268
00:17:30,560 --> 00:17:34,030
We have rules here.[br]This is not that kind of place.

269
00:17:34,240 --> 00:17:36,950
I know, but this isn't[br]how it looks at all...

270
00:17:37,160 --> 00:17:39,590
...because Rick is my husband.

271
00:17:40,120 --> 00:17:41,260
Oh, really?

272
00:17:41,480 --> 00:17:43,550
You'd better tell his other wife.

273
00:17:43,760 --> 00:17:46,190
She called three times[br]asking where he is.

274
00:17:48,880 --> 00:17:51,310
Yes, I will tell her.

275
00:17:54,000 --> 00:17:55,870
So you didn't leave the bank?

276
00:17:56,680 --> 00:18:00,350
And somehow we ended up[br]with a joint checking account.

277
00:18:01,680 --> 00:18:03,670
What will you ever use that for?

278
00:18:03,880 --> 00:18:06,310
To pay for the gym.

279
00:18:09,560 --> 00:18:11,470
So I had a great day.

280
00:18:11,680 --> 00:18:13,950
Rick and I hit it off.[br]We were making out.

281
00:18:14,200 --> 00:18:17,270
Then my boss walked in[br]and fired me for being a whore.

282
00:18:18,840 --> 00:18:20,430
- You got fired?[br]- Oh, my gosh!

283
00:18:20,680 --> 00:18:24,350
It's so weird. I have never[br]been fired from anything.

284
00:18:24,600 --> 00:18:26,110
Sweetie.

285
00:18:26,360 --> 00:18:30,190
I started walking around,[br]not knowing what to do next.

286
00:18:30,440 --> 00:18:34,870
I started asking people on the street[br]if they wanted massages.

287
00:18:35,280 --> 00:18:38,110
Then these policemen thought[br]I was a whore too.

288
00:18:38,400 --> 00:18:40,990
It's really been a bad day,[br]whore-wise.

289
00:18:46,520 --> 00:18:48,550
Hey, Duck.[br]Is Chick here?

290
00:18:52,280 --> 00:18:53,910
Yeah, Bunny Rabbit.

291
00:18:55,400 --> 00:18:57,150
Ready for our last practice?

292
00:18:57,400 --> 00:19:01,350
We're not getting that spin right[br]because my place is too small.

293
00:19:01,560 --> 00:19:04,870
- Want to use our place?[br]- No, I had another idea.

294
00:19:45,360 --> 00:19:46,580
We did it!

295
00:19:47,160 --> 00:19:48,830
That was incredible!

296
00:19:49,080 --> 00:19:52,430
That was amazing![br]We totally nailed it!

297
00:19:52,640 --> 00:19:55,470
Hey, listen.[br]Thanks a lot, Tribbiani.

298
00:19:56,000 --> 00:19:57,750
Oh, my God![br]Look at the time.

299
00:19:58,000 --> 00:19:59,950
I got to catch the bus to the ball.

300
00:20:02,880 --> 00:20:04,310
Good luck.

301
00:20:04,560 --> 00:20:08,390
Unless you want to practice[br]the fox trot. Or the tango?

302
00:20:08,760 --> 00:20:11,030
Thanks, but no.

303
00:20:11,880 --> 00:20:14,870
You see, I think I'm ready[br]to dance with girls.

304
00:20:16,920 --> 00:20:19,110
- Go get them, Treeger.[br]- Right.

305
00:20:24,920 --> 00:20:26,790
You want to come?[br]Marge has a friend.

306
00:20:27,920 --> 00:20:28,900
Really?

307
00:20:29,160 --> 00:20:31,670
You'd dance good with her.[br]She's the same size as me.

308
00:20:32,080 --> 00:20:33,510
No, I'm good.

309
00:20:50,800 --> 00:20:53,430
It looks like you've got[br]great experience.

310
00:20:53,640 --> 00:20:55,830
Let's see.[br]Reason for leaving last job?

311
00:20:56,040 --> 00:20:57,750
They thought I was a whore.

312
00:20:59,520 --> 00:21:02,950
Okay. We'll give you a call[br]if anything comes up.

313
00:21:04,360 --> 00:21:06,740
Great. Thank you very much.

